{"tid":1683992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"去台灣除咗入台證，仲有種叫入出境許可證，可以留半年","createTime":"2019-10-31T01:34:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T00:27:12.000Z","uid":39277,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a5514ab892fbe7ec2bcaefb2a097eefda5009031","tid":1683992,"uid":39277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T01:34:08.000Z","msg":"最近認識咗一位香港移居去台灣嘅朋友，佢移居咗去台灣幾年，喺𠴱邊落地生根，娶妻育兒。<br />\n<br />\n佢心繫香港，都好關心香港嘅事，接觸有啲受事件影響去到台灣嘅手足。<br />\n<br />\n我同佢就傾咗好耐，有啲資訊想提供畀一啲想到台灣散心一排長時間嘅爸絲打啦！<br />\n<br />\n除咗入台證，有種叫<span style=\"color: red;\">入出境許可證</span>嘅簽證，可以喺台灣境內逗留長達半年時間，可能有人知道依種簽證，但係我都share出嚟<br />\n<br />\n等五日時間，成功審批後，可以hold 住，出發先畀錢,print出嚟就用得。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.sostaiwan.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sostaiwan.com&d=VY3E9QkOBFFWjsPhNJvPHqcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=1d5341b9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.sostaiwan.com</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s9RztYF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs9RztYF.png&h=3cad1ade&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1xu2iG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1xu2iG.png&h=3fa8aff2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3n9pRb2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3n9pRb2.png&h=74bffe76&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y8UM4w2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy8UM4w2.png&h=ba566f2b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vmp5ADJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVmp5ADJ.png&h=891900d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n位台灣朋友識好多人，佢話好多高官表面扮無野，實則震過貓王，嚟緊好多外資公司都搬去新加圾，走資情況空前嚴重，再係咁香港企業可以執一半。<br />\n<br />\n識得諗嘅差佬都搞移民，因為交人就一定，但係佢地唔敢話自己做警察，好多國家都唔收佢地。"},{"pid":"d8ae5c5bbb47dbe6dbb35aea6679bb196884426e","tid":1683992,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T01:39:40.000Z","msg":"唔怪得坡狗出盡力打壓"},{"pid":"f60969e019c96ef92eae290e7f0332eb3866eb82","tid":1683992,"uid":39277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T01:45:39.000Z","msg":"推畀一啲想臨時去台灣散心嘅朋友睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44b2565abed882cad7828809bd48637d75a311b4","tid":1683992,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T01:48:43.000Z","msg":"聽聞好多人已經開定離岸存款戶口<br />\n只要㩒一㩒制<br />\n就可以將錢轉去外國"},{"pid":"f87a6f1fb130a1fbfe85ee94d1eed5574eaaee99","tid":1683992,"uid":83102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44b2565abed882cad7828809bd48637d75a311b4","tid":1683992,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T01:48:43.000Z","msg":"聽聞好多人已經開定離岸存款戶口<br />\n只要㩒一㩒制<br />\n就可以將錢轉去外國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T01:56:11.000Z","msg":"好多朋友係ib投資美股<br />\n入面禁幾粒制<br />\n極低手續費換錢"},{"pid":"ddc6f1fb4457825d16ecef507cd732b97692dc8e","tid":1683992,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T02:23:16.000Z","msg":"加拿大免簽6個月"},{"pid":"35b9556e34e797e07273773847aa59ce470c3432","tid":1683992,"uid":31920,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T02:33:44.000Z","msg":"成個時代革命<br />\n最唔想就係比二奶坡仔漁人得利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人要加油<br />\n光復後要努力係坡仔手中攞番屬於哋嘅野<br />\n一係努力，攬埋星加坡齊齊炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3401a5ea2d4370bca820c4f30f916e1e1138702b","tid":1683992,"uid":39277,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddc6f1fb4457825d16ecef507cd732b97692dc8e","tid":1683992,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T02:23:16.000Z","msg":"加拿大免簽6個月"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:02:35.000Z","msg":"人生路不熟<br />\n生活指數貴<br />\n唔係人人負擔到<br />\n<br />\n有好多手足銀彈有限<br />\n而且台灣都有班有心人提供支援"},{"pid":"74d622532f38ac7f3007a5ef7d71a76c227091dc","tid":1683992,"uid":189047,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:34:53.000Z","msg":"唔比打工無收入😭<br />\n<br />\n咁自己做老細又得唔得？"},{"pid":"ff75853d53a2ace9958a4a90122e833c70cd96a0","tid":1683992,"uid":39277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74d622532f38ac7f3007a5ef7d71a76c227091dc","tid":1683992,"uid":189047,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:34:53.000Z","msg":"唔比打工無收入😭<br />\n<br />\n咁自己做老細又得唔得？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:38:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4774abf8253c4123fe271a31ae9c0e13b3bf3626","tid":1683992,"uid":131767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T04:12:42.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c14c4a52a3155a5882461ab8828f06ddb27cda","tid":1683992,"uid":21641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T04:16:36.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"2ced2791130109ed591c3d66e6466957d9b6728b","tid":1683992,"uid":128489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T04:20:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"325591e1a9ce87aeb457b7637837ef97be77ba4e","tid":1683992,"uid":39277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ced2791130109ed591c3d66e6466957d9b6728b","tid":1683992,"uid":128489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T04:20:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T04:42:02.000Z","msg":"依層唔係太清楚<br />\n留番畀其他爸絲打答"},{"pid":"2a65d3ddd4078a83a7dbcb6a89f65faafd07f197","tid":1683992,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T04:49:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/04EdLjM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F04EdLjM.gif&h=e7e4e8ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e20503ac9bcbd5aac39e6ef4cef0c6be1ff7120"